A robotics startup flies a small drone above its booth for attention, enhancing the vibrant atmosphere of the fair. Additionally, a data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance. The dean stops by to thank recruiters for supporting the university, while camera crews from the university media team capture interviews. In the adjoining classroom, workshops on networking etiquette begin.
